scene.message:
Nanjo: We'll all be exam{nl}
students soon enough.{waitkey}I, of course, intend to pass{nl}
into my first-choice school{nl}
at the top of the class.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, let's just hurry{nl}
up and get to the hospital.{nl}
No detours allowed, y'know.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You thinking about{nl}
your future at all? Me, I'm{nl}
not planning to take any{nl}
entrance exams, though.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I don't wanna go to{nl}
cram school~ I just wanna{nl}
sleep at home all day~{waitkey}{ret}

Student: No way, you gotta{nl}
study. Let's meet up{wait_fr:21}, 'kay?{nl}
The subway ticket gate?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: The subway...{wait_fr:21} you go{nl}
north through Sun Mall, then{nl}
straight right, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: They say the{nl}
"Persona Game" lets you see{nl}
what you'll look like in{nl}
the future.{waitkey}Maybe I'll try it and take a{nl}
peek at my future self too~{waitkey}Wonder if I'll really be a{nl}
college student by this time{nl}
next year...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Ugh, how pathetic!{nl}
If you've got time for the{nl}
"Persona Game," you should{nl}
be studying!{waitkey}We promised we'd go to the{nl}
same college together...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Idiot!{waitkey}{ret}
